OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,FThe family of the late Ricky Hatton
OL,7,Fhave revealed plans to take part in a
OL,8,Fspecial boxing event in his memory.
OL,10,FRicky's son Campbell Hatton, his
OL,11,Fnephew Jack Hatton and niece Lola
OL,12,FHatton will be part of a fundraising
OL,13,Fshow in Dubai in April.
OL,15,FThe proceeds will support the Ricky
OL,16,FHatton Foundation, a mental health
OL,17,Fcharity formed after Hatton took his
OL,18,Fown life aged 46 at his home in Hyde,
OL,19,FGreater Manchester, on 14 September.
