OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,FThe boxer had been due to fly out to
OL,7,FDubai after announcing he was coming
OL,8,Fout of retirement to face fellow
OL,9,Fveteran Eisa Al Dah in a middleweight
OL,10,Fcontest, on the day he was found dead.
OL,12,F"He should still be here topping the
OL,13,Fbill. It's still bittersweet, but I'm
OL,14,Fjust glad we can all do it in his
OL,15,Fmemory," Campbell said.
OL,17,FCampbell's cousins, Lola and Jack are
OL,18,Fin the beginning stages of their
OL,19,Famateur boxing careers.
