OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,FLola said: "I feel blessed really
OL,7,Fbecause we've got such a good
OL,8,Fopportunity and it wouldn't be
OL,9,Fpossible if it weren't for him, so it
OL,10,Fmeans a lot to me."
OL,12,FShe added: "Hopefully we can do him
OL,13,Fproud, all three of us, Campbell, me,
OL,14,FJack, and hopefully we can all put a
OL,15,Fgood performance in and he'll be
OL,16,Fwatching us from up there."
OL,18,F"He'd be really proud of us all. It'll
OL,19,Fbe good because we're boxing in his
OL,20,Fmemory," Jack said.
