OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,F"I didn't think I'd ever see the day
OL,7,Fwhere, like me, Lola, and Campbell
OL,8,Fwould all be on the same undercard. So
OL,9,Fthat's the main thing, we're all like
OL,10,Fworking together as a family."
OL,12,FCampbell says he is looking forward to
OL,13,Fthe fight which will be a "good day
OL,14,Ffor the foundation and it's a good day
OL,15,Ffor the family" as it will be a great
OL,16,Fopportunity to get the trio on the
OL,17,Fcard.
OL,19,FHe added: "It's been something to aim
OL,20,Ffor, and I want to do it in memory of
OL,21,Fmy dad.
