OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,F"I've had a bad 12 months really where
OL,7,FI've lost a few of my friends and
OL,8,Fobviously what happened to my dad to
OL,9,Ffinish the year, so I've not been in
OL,10,Fthe best of places.
OL,12,F"So I think doing something like this
OL,13,Fjust to get my head back right more
OL,14,Fthan anything, to be honest, but I'm
OL,15,Ffeeling loads better.
OL,17,F"I think when you're training and
OL,18,Fyou're moving towards something, it
OL,19,Fhelps you a lot. So it's done me the
OL,20,Fworld of good."
