OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,FPrior to the announcement of Ricky's
OL,7,Fdeath, United Arab Emirates boxer Eisa
OL,8,FAl Dah said he was in the shower
OL,9,Fgetting ready for Ricky Hatton to land
OL,10,Fin Dubai.
OL,12,FThey were due to meet that night, and
OL,13,Fthe next day, they were meant to be
OL,14,Fholding a press conference together.
OL,16,FHe said: "I thought it was a joke, no
OL,17,Fway. It really hurt my heart, and all
OL,18,Fthe things surprised me."
