OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,FEisa, who is a pioneer in establishing
OL,7,Fthe professional boxing scene in the
OL,8,FUAE said that Ricky supported his
OL,9,Fvision of inspiring children through
OL,10,Fboxing too.
OL,12,FAfter Ricky died, he says he had to do
OL,13,Fit and still fight not just a regular
OL,14,Ffight.
OL,16,FEisa Al Dah said he told Kell Brook:
OL,17,F"It is not about who wins or who loses
OL,18,Fthe fight. It's just about Ricky
OL,19,FHatton. I want to put the best of the
OL,20,Fbest out and let's build a nice story
OL,21,Fbehind it.
