OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,F"Let's make everybody proud about me,
OL,7,Fproud about you, and Ricky, he's proud
OL,8,Fabout us, for what we did for boxing."
OL,10,FIt was Eisa Al Dah's first time in
OL,11,FRicky Hatton's gym: "It is my pleasure
OL,12,Fto be in his gym. I'm so excited but
OL,13,Fat the same time I'm sad. I wish I
OL,14,Fcould see him and we could train
OL,15,Ftogether."
OL,17,FKell Brook: "It was a no brainer (to
OL,18,Ffight) for Ricky Hatton. With what he
OL,19,Fwent through in the last part of his
OL,20,Flife, and what he'd been through for a
OL,21,Fwhile.
