OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,F"Because I've been through the same `
OL,7,Fdepression, addiction, mental health.
OL,8,FSo the message is for people who are
OL,9,Fstruggling...it's alright not to be
OL,10,Fokay and to reach out.
OL,12,F"Because when men try to keep things
OL,13,Fin, it sometimes eats them up.
OL,15,F"I knew myself for many years, the
OL,16,Fstruggle. And you get to a stage where
OL,17,Fyou surrender and reach out, and it's
OL,18,Fthe best thing that I've ever done,
OL,19,Fbecause I'm in a very good place now.
