OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,F"This fight is for Ricky and for the
OL,7,Fpeople struggling."
OL,9,FKell Brook: "I think he'd have a smile
OL,10,Fand he'd pat me on the back and say
OL,11,F'go on lad get on with it, get it
OL,12,Fdone.'
OL,14,F"I'm excited, the family that is on
