OL,3,C'He'll be watching us from up there':
OL,4,CBoxing event in Ricky Hatton's memory
OL,6,FKel Brook, from Sheffield, has not
OL,7,Fboxed for four years since he fought
OL,8,FBoltonian Amir Khan.
OL,10,FHe has come out of retirement for this
OL,11,Ffight, and has been back training and
OL,12,Fdieting. He says when he is training
OL,13,FRicky always comes into his mind,
OL,14,F"this is why I'm doing it," he added.
OL,16,F"He was an inspiration to me, an idol
OL,17,Fto me, a icon in boxing. To be asked
OL,18,Fto do this fight for Ricky, it means
OL,19,Fso much to me, so I'm gonna make sure
OL,20,Fthat it counts," said Kel Brook.
